CDISC Standardization of nonstandard data

SelectEX <- c("STUDYID", "DOMAIN", "USUBJID", "EXTRT", "EXDOSE", "EXDOSU", "EXROUTE", 
                 "EXSTDTC", "EXENDTC",  "VISIT", "VISITNUM")
SelectPC <- c("STUDYID", "DOMAIN", "USUBJID", "PCSEQ", "PCGRPID", "PCSPID", "PCTESTCD", 
            "PCTEST", "PCCAT", "PCSCAT", "PCORRES", "PCORRESU", "PCSTRESC", "PCSTRESN",
            "PCSTRESU", "PCSTAT", "PCREASND", "PCNAM", "PCSPEC", "PCMETHOD", "PCFAST", 
            "PCDRVFL", "PCLLOQ", "PCULOQ", "VISITNUM", "VISIT", "PCDTC", "PCTPT", 
            "PCTPTNUM", "PCRFTDTC")
Var_STUDYID <- "SKI2670_EMSD_I_2013"
Var_VISIT <- "TREATMENT"
EX_SKI2670 <- skdata[[35]] %>% NomActTime() %>% 
                  select(Subject_No, Treatment, Nominal_Time, Actual_Time, Fasting) %>% 
    rename(USUBJID = Subject_No, EXSTDTC = Actual_Time) %>% 
    mutate(STUDYID = Var_STUDYID, ###
           DOMAIN = "EX",
           EXTRT = ifelse(Treatment == "Placebo", "PLACEBO", "SKI2670"), ###
           EXDOSE = ifelse(Treatment == "Placebo", 0, gsub(" mg", "",Treatment)),
           EXDOSU = "mg",
           EXENDTC = EXSTDTC,
           EXROUTE = "ORAL",
           VISIT = Var_VISIT,
           VISITNUM = "1") %>% 
    mutate(EXSTDTC = gsub(" ", "T", EXSTDTC)) %>% 
    mutate(EXENDTC = gsub(" ", "T", EXENDTC)) %>% 
    select_(.dots = SelectEX)
write.csv(EX_SKI2670, "SDTM/EX.csv", row.names = FALSE)
#kable(EX_SKI2670)
sknca_src <- read.csv("data/sknca_src.csv", stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
PC_SKI2670 <- sknca_src %>% rename(USUBJID = Subject_No, PCSTRESN = Value) %>% 
    mutate(STUDYID = Var_STUDYID, 
           DOMAIN = "PC",
           PCFAST = "Y",
           PCSPID = "NORMAL",
           PCTESTCD = "SKI2670",
           PCGRPID = PCTESTCD,
           PCTEST = paste0("CONCENTRATION OF ", PCTESTCD),
           PCCAT = "ANALYTE",
           PCSCAT = "PARENT",
           PCORRES = PCSTRESN, 
           PCSTRESC = PCSTRESN,
           PCSTRESU = "ng/mL",
           PCORRESU = PCSTRESU, 
           PCSTAT = "", 
           PCREASND = "", 
           PCNAM = "BIOCORE CO LTD",
           PCSPEC = "PLASMA",
           PCMETHOD = "HPLC/MS/MS", 
           PCDRVFL = "",
           PCLLOQ = "0.1", # 0.1 ng/ml
           PCULOQ = "300",
           VISIT = Var_VISIT,
           VISITNUM = "1",
           PCTPT = Nominal_Time,
           PCRFTDTC = EXSTDTC
           ) %>% 
    group_by(USUBJID) %>% 
    mutate(PCTPTNUM = row_number(Nominal_Time)) %>% ungroup() %>%
    mutate(PCSEQ = row_number()) %>% 
    mutate(PCDTC = gsub(" ", "T", PCDTC)) %>% 
    mutate(PCRFTDTC = gsub(" ", "T", PCRFTDTC)) %>% 
    select_(.dots = SelectPC)
write.csv(PC_SKI2670, "SDTM/PC.csv", row.names = FALSE)
#kable(PC_SKI2670)

        Time = "HOUR", 
        conc = "Value",
